   The xpr-libraries were created by Terence Finney (@{b}bplus@{ub}), Kenneth
Osterberg & Markus Pietz (@{b}jmodem@{ub}), Marco Papa & Stephen Walton
(@{b}kermit@{ub}), Jack Rouse (@{b}quickb@{ub}), Marc Boucher (@{b}xmodem@{ub}), Ueli
